oai_dc:dc.dc:title: 849ers Banquet
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: McKenzie, Robert G.
oai_dc:dc.dc:publisher: Heritage Protocol, Florida State University, Tallahassee, Florida.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The photos in this collection surround the activities of the male students who lived in barracks building 849 on the FSU West Campus at the former Dale Mabry field. The men, who referred to themselves as the "849ers," bonded together in a pseudo-fraternity they called Theta Delta Iota.
Robert G. McKenzie was a Florida State University student, class of 1954. These photographs make up the Robert G. McKenzie Photograph Collection (Accession No. HP-2010-002). B/W; aprox. 5x7.
